# Interview Practice Project

Personal interview preparation across three pillars: algorithm (LeetCode 75), system design, and behavioral interviews.

## Key Files

- `interview-tracker.md` — progress tracker with checkboxes, recap log, and exam log
- `FOCUS.md` — growth goals and weekly practice cadence
- `CONTRIBUTING.md` — how to write and organize notes

## Note Standards

When creating or editing notes in this repository, follow `CONTRIBUTING.md`:

- One interview concept per file
- Concise, recall-oriented writing with examples and diagrams when useful
- Lowercase kebab-case filenames
- Capture mistakes and corrections from practice sessions

## Skills

Use project skills when the user asks for practice:

- **interview-learning** — one new item per session with a practice test
- **interview-recap** — retention recaps, daily reviews, and monthly exams
